"plugin. You can also specify a URL to install a plugin bundle from a "
"remote source."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/plugins.rst:265
msgid ""
"Note: When **RequirePluginSignature** is `true` - plugin uploads cannot "
"be enabled, and may only be installed via the Marketplace (which verifies"
